## Broadcast Modes

| Mode | Source | Music | Transition |
|------|--------|-------|------------|
| **Radio Mode** | Cloud VPS running OBS 24/7 | 100% volume | Default state |
| **Live Mode** | Local laptop OBS | 50% background | E.I. Werner goes live |

When E.I. Werner ends a live stream, the broadcast returns to Radio Mode automatically. The Inn is always open.

---

## Uptime Target

**99.95%** — achieved through:

- Dual internet pipes with automatic failover
- Battery backup for laptop and router
- Hardware encoding (GPU, not CPU)
- Remote monitoring and recovery procedures
- Cloud VPS for Radio Mode (not dependent on local machine)

